This sucks!

00:43.501 --> 00:45.253
[sighs]

00:45.295 --> 00:47.589
Yes. Yes, it does.

00:56.639 --> 00:58.224
[sighs] All right.

00:58.266 --> 01:00.393
Today is gonna be really hard.

01:00.435 --> 01:02.228
We're gonna
get through it together, okay?

01:02.270 --> 01:03.938
We're gonna make him proud.

01:03.980 --> 01:05.940
We are not gonna let them win.

01:05.982 --> 01:07.108
Who's "them"?

01:07.150 --> 01:08.693
The terrorists, honey.

01:08.735 --> 01:11.905
Sorry.
I thought you understood.

01:11.946 --> 01:13.239
[sighs]

01:13.281 --> 01:20.413
<i>♪ ♪</i>

01:27.504 --> 01:29.964
Do you think it's fair
that I get to have his chain

01:30.006 --> 01:31.466
and Casey doesn't?

01:31.508 --> 01:34.761
I don't even think
she knows what's going on.

01:34.803 --> 01:35.804
I think you're good.

01:37.681 --> 01:40.517
You know, I don't even
think we have to tell her.

01:40.558 --> 01:42.477
I mean, do you--do you
think we should tell her?

01:42.519 --> 01:44.938
We could tell her
I'm her dad.

01:44.979 --> 01:46.940
Do you think
she'll find out what happened?

01:46.981 --> 01:48.316
Nah.

01:54.239 --> 01:56.408
We're so late.
Come on, honey.

02:17.470 --> 02:20.140
Sorry we're late. MapQuest.

02:20.181 --> 02:22.767
Oh, you have nothing
to apologize for.

02:22.809 --> 02:25.270
Hey, do you need a Xanax?
I brought enough for everybody.

02:25.311 --> 02:28.314
No, um, that's okay.

02:28.356 --> 02:30.150
Somebody's getting married.

02:30.191 --> 02:33.111
[Wagner's "Bridal Chorus"
playing]

02:33.153 --> 02:40.285
