in our darkest times,

03:05.185 --> 03:07.020
there is always joy,

03:07.062 --> 03:08.813
there is always light.

03:08.855 --> 03:10.315
- Not.
- Peter!

03:10.357 --> 03:13.401
Shh!
[crowd murmuring]

03:14.986 --> 03:16.529
Anyway...

03:16.571 --> 03:18.031
[whispering]
Did you hear what I said?

03:18.073 --> 03:20.325
I said, "Not."

03:20.367 --> 03:23.203
I heard what you said.
It was hysterical.

03:23.244 --> 03:24.954
But don't talk like that.

03:24.996 --> 03:27.332
This is a house of God.
Watch your friggin' mouth.

03:27.374 --> 03:29.292
There is always light,

03:29.334 --> 03:31.211
there's always joy.

03:31.252 --> 03:33.046
Looking good.

03:33.088 --> 03:35.048
Okay.

03:35.090 --> 03:36.716
All right, little man.

03:36.758 --> 03:38.677
I'm gonna need you
to smile for the camera.

03:38.718 --> 03:41.388
Come on.
Help me out here.

03:41.429 --> 03:42.681
What's your problem?

03:42.722 --> 03:44.432
