04:02.075 --> 04:04.494
<i>[beat playing in background]</i>

04:06.246 --> 04:07.497
Amy.

04:07.539 --> 04:09.916
- I'm so sorry for your loss.
- Thank you.

04:09.958 --> 04:11.626
Please let me know
if there's anything I can do.

04:11.668 --> 04:13.336
I will.
Thank you.

04:13.378 --> 04:14.963
