04:20.468 --> 04:22.137
- Lori, please.
- What?

04:22.178 --> 04:23.346
I love you.

04:23.388 --> 04:25.098
We're gonna have
to talk about this.

04:25.140 --> 04:26.683
- I gotta go.
- [sighs]

04:29.227 --> 04:30.228
Here, honey.
No. Come here.

04:30.270 --> 04:31.563
Put this down.

04:31.604 --> 04:33.773
How ya doing?
Are you okay?

04:33.815 --> 04:35.358
Hey, hey, hey.
How are we doing?

04:35.400 --> 04:36.693
Uh, it's quite a party.

04:36.735 --> 04:37.777
- Yeah?
- Yeah.

04:37.819 --> 04:40.447
- I gotta pee.
- Oh, yeah? okay.

04:40.488 --> 04:41.614
