05:33.708 --> 05:35.627
Boop, boop, boop.

05:39.214 --> 05:40.757
[snorting loudly]

05:45.553 --> 05:48.139
Do as I say,
not as I do, okay?

05:54.229 --> 05:56.106
[door opens]

05:56.147 --> 05:58.733
- Mm. Oh, yo.
- Hey.

05:58.775 --> 06:00.819
- What's up, big boy? Huh?
- How you doing?

06:00.860 --> 06:02.320
- You look good.
- Yeah?

06:02.362 --> 06:03.780
It's been forever.
Yeah, man.

06:03.822 --> 06:05.073
You're out there
fucking killing it.

06:05.115 --> 06:06.658
- Jesus Christ.
- What are you doing?

06:06.700 --> 06:07.867
- How you doing?
- I'm good.

06:07.909 --> 06:09.994
You know, I'm just
doing the best I can.

06:10.036 --> 06:11.996
The fuck is this guy--
these fucking Russians, man.

06:12.038 --> 06:13.998
They make me want
to kill myself.

06:14.040 --> 06:14.916
All right, already.

06:14.958 --> 06:15.959
You know what?
That's it. Send.

06:16.001 --> 06:17.544
Done. I'm done.

06:17.585 --> 06:19.462
- So...
- What is it you do again?

06:19.504 --> 06:22.173
I know you explained it.
I can never retain it.

06:22.215 --> 06:24.426
I work for a Russian bank.
It doesn't matter.

06:24.467 --> 06:26.011
Does that suck?
It sounds like it sucks.

06:26.052 --> 06:27.387
I mean,
it doesn't always suck.

06:27.429 --> 06:28.930
I mean,
I still get to go to Russia.

06:28.972 --> 06:31.516
Every time I do, I still put
on the "Rocky IV" soundtrack,

06:31.558 --> 06:33.476
get ready for it--
still works pretty good.

06:33.518 --> 06:34.894
I don't know. Fuck it.

06:34.936 --> 06:36.563
- Get me a beer.
- Okay.

06:36.604 --> 06:39.065
- I love you. Good to see you.
- You too.

06:39.107 --> 06:40.567
Hey.

06:42.610 --> 06:45.113
