<i>[jazzy music playing]</i>

06:45.155 --> 06:47.490
Me and my dad are gonna see
the new "Jimmy Neutron" movie.

06:47.532 --> 06:50.493
That's cool.
My dad is dead.

06:50.535 --> 06:52.328
Yeah, my dad
told me about that.

06:52.370 --> 06:54.456
He said that your dad went
into a burning building

06:54.497 --> 06:56.249
and saved a bunch of people.

06:56.291 --> 06:57.917
- And then he died.
- Yeah.

06:57.959 --> 07:00.253
He was just being a hero
and stuff, I guess.

07:00.295 --> 07:03.757
I'm gonna miss Uncle Scott.
He was really cool.

07:03.798 --> 07:05.759
Maybe all the uncles
can be your dad.

07:05.800 --> 07:07.469
You could have,
like, five dads.

07:08.803 --> 07:10.430
Okay, here we go.

07:10.472 --> 07:13.224
One, two, three.

07:13.266 --> 07:14.559
Boop!

07:14.601 --> 07:16.436
Mom, he's making
finger penises again.

07:16.478 --> 07:18.605
- Come on.
- Hey, Peter. Come on.

07:18.646 --> 07:20.106
Let's take a good one now, okay?

07:20.148 --> 07:22.609
And then we'll have fun later.
What'd I say?

07:22.650 --> 07:24.778
Do as I say,
not as I do.

07:24.819 --> 07:26.154
- There it is.
- What does that mean?

07:26.196 --> 07:27.489
Here we go.
Don't worry about it.

07:27.530 --> 07:29.908
Everyone, say cheese!

07:29.949 --> 07:32.744
- all: Cheese!
- Smokin'!

07:32.786 --> 07:34.454
All right, that's it.
I'm going to get a drink.

07:34.496 --> 07:36.831
Hey, we'll try again later.

07:38.249 --> 07:41.127
Peter, will you please
stop ruining these photographs?

07:41.169 --> 07:44.297
We are gonna be looking
at these for a very long time.

07:44.339 --> 07:46.049
Hey, hey.
Hey, buddy.

07:46.091 --> 07:48.301
Hey. Let's have
a little talk, okay?

07:48.343 --> 07:49.844
I got him.

07:52.430 --> 07:54.015
Oh, Peter.

07:54.057 --> 07:56.476
You know
I've been praying for you.

07:56.518 --> 07:58.061
Sometimes in life,

07:58.103 --> 08:01.648
we feel that
there's a shadow following us,

08:01.690 --> 08:04.901
and this darkness
comes over us.

08:04.943 --> 08:07.153
That could turn into fear.

08:07.195 --> 08:10.407
What if this darkness
never goes away?

08:10.448 --> 08:13.118
But only later
do we realize

08:13.159 --> 08:15.912
that the shadow
is actually the hand of God

08:15.954 --> 08:18.998
guiding us and protecting us.

08:19.040 --> 08:22.377
See, God,
He needed your dad up there.

08:22.419 --> 08:25.046
He died on the 11th, right?

08:25.088 --> 08:28.091
3 times 11 is 33.

08:28.133 --> 08:29.551
Three.

08:29.592 --> 08:33.346
Father, son,
the Holy Ghost, right?

08:33.388 --> 08:38.852
Christ was 33 when He died,
same age as your father.

08:38.893 --> 08:41.563
Your dad is Jesus incarnate.

08:41.604 --> 08:44.858
Okay? You are never alone, sir.

08:44.899 --> 08:45.984
Your dad is--
[slams table]

08:46.026 --> 08:48.903
he's right here in his room!

08:48.945 --> 08:49.988
He is.

08:50.030 --> 08:51.698
You could say hello to him.

08:51.740 --> 08:53.199
Say hello to your father.

08:53.241 --> 08:54.534
- Uh--
- Say hi.

08:54.576 --> 08:55.910
Don't be shy.

08:55.952 --> 08:58.246
- Hi, Dad.
- Oh.

08:58.288 --> 09:01.291
Did you feel his presence?

09:01.332 --> 09:02.959
Did you? I did.

09:03.001 --> 09:05.170
What was he, 6'3",
full of muscle?

09:05.211 --> 09:08.214
Your dad, he's right here.
[slams table]

09:08.256 --> 09:09.716
Your dad was a hero!

09:09.758 --> 09:12.260
He's here. He's a hero.
Do you understand?

09:12.302 --> 09:14.929
I want to thank you
for your service, sir.

09:14.971 --> 09:16.514
And thank you for not letting

09:16.556 --> 09:20.060
those dirty scumbag
Talibanians win.

09:24.105 --> 09:25.065
Aw, fuck.

09:25.106 --> 09:27.484
Should we get another round?

09:27.525 --> 09:28.777
Uh, yeah.

09:28.818 --> 09:30.403
- What is it, Saturday?
- Yeah.

09:30.445 --> 09:32.072
Yeah, fuck it.
Angela's soccer season's over.

09:32.113 --> 09:34.032
Did you hear? They got
into the semifinals this year.

09:34.074 --> 09:35.408
- Angela got in the semifinals?
- Yeah.

09:35.450 --> 09:36.534
- That's crazy.
- Yeah.

09:36.576 --> 09:38.161
Next year,
we should get to states.

09:38.203 --> 09:39.913
- Yeah, that's awesome.
- Yeah. Whatever.

09:39.954 --> 09:41.706
It's fucking girls' soccer, right?

09:41.748 --> 09:43.333
- I mean--
- Well, it's your daughter.

09:43.375 --> 09:44.709
I know. I like her.

09:44.751 --> 09:46.670
I fucking love her.

09:46.711 --> 09:48.296
She's good.
She's a good kid.

09:48.338 --> 09:49.464
- Yeah.
- Yeah.

09:49.506 --> 09:52.258
She's--yeah, she's fine.

09:52.300 --> 09:53.510
What do you mean?
Are you good?

09:53.551 --> 09:54.636
Yeah--no.

09:54.678 --> 09:55.929
I don't know.
I don't know.

09:55.970 --> 09:57.430
I don't know what the fuck
is going on anymore.

09:57.472 --> 09:59.432
Like, I used to think I knew,
but I don't know.

09:59.474 --> 10:00.767
I mean, your aunt and I

10:00.809 --> 10:02.268
