10:07.565 --> 10:09.109
Fucking where are we here?

10:09.150 --> 10:11.236
Fucking Staten Island.
I'm not going to therapy.

10:11.277 --> 10:12.612
I'm not getting divorced,
all right?

10:12.654 --> 10:14.114
I just don't know
what's going on.

10:14.155 --> 10:16.700
I don't understand what
the fuck is going on anymore.

10:16.741 --> 10:18.284
You'll see when you get older.

10:18.326 --> 10:20.662
- What does that mean?
- You'll see.

10:20.704 --> 10:22.497
I'm good.
Just get me another beer?

10:22.539 --> 10:23.748
- Yeah.
- All right.

10:23.790 --> 10:25.333
Don't worry about me.
I'm fucking chill.

10:32.424 --> 10:35.343
[indistinct chatter]

10:35.385 --> 10:36.845
Hey.

10:36.886 --> 10:38.304
What are you doing?

10:38.346 --> 10:40.306
Come on.
I gotta go run an errand.

10:40.348 --> 10:43.101
I gotta go get some cigarettes.

10:43.143 --> 10:45.770
- How you doing, bro?
- How am I doing?

10:45.812 --> 10:49.441
I'm fucking--
what the fuck, you know?

10:49.482 --> 10:51.609
That's who I want to be with
for the rest of my life, okay?

10:51.651 --> 10:53.695
But god damn it! Fuck!

10:53.737 --> 10:55.447
This is it, bro.
That's it.

10:55.488 --> 10:57.073
I don't know
what else to tell you.

10:57.115 --> 10:59.367
Unless you went to end up
divorced, living on a futon,

10:59.409 --> 11:00.744
