the George Jefferson. Watch.

11:27.854 --> 11:30.815
[snorting loudly]

11:30.857 --> 11:32.150
You like movies, Pete?

11:32.192 --> 11:33.735
You see that "Beautiful Mind"?

11:33.777 --> 11:36.780
That Russell Crowe is amazing.
