11:36.821 --> 11:38.865
Unbelievable.

11:38.907 --> 11:40.658
You into girls yet?

11:40.700 --> 11:42.243
You will be.
You will be.

11:45.330 --> 11:47.832
- [nasally] Hey. Hey.
- There he is.

11:47.874 --> 11:49.959
- Yeah, buddy.
