and everything.

12:08.353 --> 12:09.479
I got it in the garage.

12:09.521 --> 12:11.106
<i>[Creed's "My Sacrifice"
playing]</i>

12:11.147 --> 12:12.982
Are you fucking kidding me?

12:13.024 --> 12:15.443
Listen to me, Peter.
You hear this song?

12:15.485 --> 12:18.363
This is a great song
by a group called Creed.

12:18.405 --> 12:19.906
Remember that name.
You know, people think

12:19.948 --> 12:21.408
that this is religious crap.

12:21.449 --> 12:22.325
Bullshit, man.

12:22.367 --> 12:24.119
